description: Planning officials unanimously turn down proposals for a treatment facility in Laxey.
title: Laxey sewage treatment works rejection 'a victory for the people'
title_page: Laxey sewage treatment works rejection 'a victory for the people' - BBC News
maintext: Alan Clague, who campaigned against the plan, told the Local Democracy Reporting Service the rejection was a "good day for Laxey", but added that he hoped MU would return with a new plan that could be "supported by the residents".
